snippet: Palestinians clashed with Israeli soldiers on Friday at demonstrations in the West Bank that were held to support a prisoner who has been on an off-again-on-again hunger strike.
abstract: Palestinians clash with Israeli soldiers at demonstrations in West Bank held to support prisoner who has been on periodic hunger strike.
